reviewText: This movie is good example of how people can live abroad without knowing the language so good and without being belong to the culture. The example funny road-trip of young Israelis, sometimes its even embarrassing. Worth watching in a case you find yourself in some other place.

As a young Israeli i am really understand the need to explore the world after long military service. This movie is reflecting whole generation of young Israelis that try to "Find themselves" and it doing it very authentic to the real situation. Very Funny!
